ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.message

Class NMD_N02

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.message.NMD_N02
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class NMD_N02
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a NMD_N02 message structure (see chapter 14.3.2). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: UAC (User Authentication Credential Segment) optional
    • 4: NMD_N02_CLOCK_AND_STATS_WITH_NOTES (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
